 class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3613714\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3613714\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ijz1665702550775.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ijz1665702550775.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ijz1665702550775.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ijz1665702550775\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Untyped\n      Library </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ijz1665702550775__untyped_library_317005\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">An Untyped Library is a Main Development Object that defines a collection of objects\n      that may be of different types, and which can be reused or accessed by other objects during\n      development or at runtime. </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ijz1665702550775__p_d96500e1_d96501e1_d96502e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kee1692183917031.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kee1692183917031.html\" title=\"Libraries are collections of objects that can be shared in some way, either during development, or at runtime. They are main development objects, so whenever they are saved or exported, all the objects that they contain are included.\">Libraries</a>.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ijz1665702550775__topic_d64542e1_d64543e1_d64544e1_d64545e1_d64546e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d893974e63\"> Characteristics </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Global objects: <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wmu1665702708557.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wmu1665702708557.html\" title=\"A Drag-and-Drop Format is Development Object that defines a default action, pop-up menu, and icon that can be used when performing drag-and-drop actions in the tree and picture widgets of forms. It is not used for drag-and-drop widgets.\">Drag-and-Drop Format</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"amz1665702708928.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/amz1665702708928.html\" title=\"A Global ProcScript is a Development Object that defines a ProcScript function that is linked into components at runtime when called by ProcScript in the component.\">Global ProcScript</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"luz1665702709079.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/luz1665702709079.html\" title=\"A Global Variable is a Development Object that defines a typed variable that can be accessed by all ProcScript in the application.\">Global Variable</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"luj1665702709292.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/luj1665702709292.html\" title=\"A Help Text is a legacy Development Object that defines a block of text that is displayed in an application window to provide help about the application. They are unlikely to be used in modern applications.\">Help Text</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vqz1665702709424.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vqz1665702709424.html\" title=\"A Menu is a Development Object that defines a Uniface menu bar, dropdown menu, or pop-up menu for a desktop application. It is cannot be used in web applications.\">Menu</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pdp1665702709496.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pdp1665702709496.html\" title=\"A Message is a Development Object that defines text to be used in the application, such as a label, help text, prompt, or error message.\">Message</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nqg1665702709724.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nqg1665702709724.html\" title=\"A Panel is a Development Object that defines a toolbar containing buttons to execute structure editor functions and operations on the active form.\">Panel</a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Translation Tables: <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sfg1665702550701.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sfg1665702550701.html\" title=\"A Device Translation Table is a Development Object that maps Uniface output to device-specific output formats for printers and character-based (CHUI) screens. It makes it possible for Uniface to support a wide variety of hardware platforms, including their output devices.\">Device Translation Table</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zxb1665702710155.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zxb1665702710155.html\" title=\"A Keyboard Translation Table is a Development Object that maps user input to structure editor functions recognized by Uniface.\">Keyboard Translation Table</a>, Language Setups (Date-Time Properties,\n                           Editor Messages, Button Text, Toggle Symbols, Japanese Era)</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Modeled properties: <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hzd1665702710226.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hzd1665702710226.html\" title=\"A Modeled Entity Interface is a Development Object that defines a reusable value for the Database Interface property of a Database Entity.\">Modeled Entity Interface</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yzg1665702711012.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yzg1665702711012.html\" title=\"A Modeled Field Interface is a Development Object that defines a reusable value for the Database Interface property of a Database Field.\">Modeled Field Interface</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ijx1665702711766.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ijx1665702711766.html\" title=\"A Modeled Field Layout is a Development Object that defines the way data is displayed.\">Modeled Field Layout</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bbr1665702712405.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bbr1665702712405.html\" title=\"A Modeled Field Syntax is a Development Object that defines some validation rules for data entry in the Field, such as the allowed characters, and field display and control attributes, such dimming and auto-jump.\">Modeled Field Syntax</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"srw1665702550375.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/srw1665702550375.html\" title=\"A Main Development Object is a Development Object that has no parent object, is maintained using a dedicated editor, and can be saved and exported as a single unit, with all its children.\">Main Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Modeled property library <code class=\"ph codeph\">LIB</code>, which is a fixed name</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Multiple runtime objects, each in its own file.</p>\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">.uar</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ijz1665702550775__table_d10733e1_d10734e1_d10735e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">lib:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ijz1665702550775__p_d96506e1_d96507e1_d96508e1\">Untyped Library specializes Main Development Object in\n            the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ijz1665702550775__li_d39248e1_d39249e1_d39250e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ijz1665702550775__p_d96509e1_d96510e1_d96511e1\">It only has properties.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ijz1665702550775__li_d39251e1_d39252e1_d39253e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ijz1665702550775__p_d96512e1_d96513e1_d96514e1\">It can contain different kinds of development\n                  objects.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ijz1665702550775__topic_d64547e1_d64548e1_d64549e1_d64550e1_d64551e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d893974e371\"> Properties </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ijz1665702550775__li_d39254e1_d39255e1_d39256e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ijz1665702550775__li_d39257e1_d39258e1_d39259e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bgv1665702551096.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Global Objects</a><p>A global object is a reusable, technology-independent object that is centrally stored and available to all components running on a given host, regardless of the deployment environment.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613714\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613714\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Untyped Library Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Untyped Library An Untyped Library is a Main Development Object that defines a collection of objects that may be of different types, and which can be reused or accessed by other objects during development or at runtime. For more information, see Libraries . Characteristics Characteristics Object type code: — Main Development Object? Yes Part of: — Contains: Property Global objects: Drag-and-Drop Format , Global ProcScript , Global Variable , Help Text , Menu , Message , Panel Translation Tables: Device Translation Table , Keyboard Translation Table , Language Setups (Date-Time Properties, Editor Messages, Button Text, Toggle Symbols, Japanese Era) Modeled properties: Modeled Entity Interface , Modeled Field Interface , Modeled Field Layout , Modeled Field Syntax Generalization: Main Development Object Specializations: Modeled property library LIB , which is a fixed name Compilation Output: Multiple runtime objects, each in its own file. .uar URI format: lib: LibraryName Untyped Library specializes Main Development Object in the following ways: It only has properties. It can contain different kinds of development objects. Properties Name Description Related Links Global Objects A global object is a reusable, technology-independent object that is centrally stored and available to all components running on a given host, regardless of the deployment environment. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}